00:56:33.590 --> 00:56:37.550
It connects your conscious mind
with your subconscious mind

00:56:37.550 --> 00:56:40.910
and gives you an
equanimity and a creativity

00:56:40.910 --> 00:56:43.670
that you ordinarily
wouldn't have.

00:56:43.670 --> 00:56:46.160
And the reason it does
that, mechanistically,

00:56:46.160 --> 00:56:51.922
the way it does it is by having
a mantra, which is a word

00:56:51.922 --> 00:56:52.880
doesn't have a meaning.

00:56:52.880 --> 00:56:55.470
It's a sound.

00:56:55.470 --> 00:56:58.070
A popular one would be "om."

00:56:58.070 --> 00:57:01.340
So you repeat that
with your breath,

00:57:01.340 --> 00:57:03.800
and that means that you
get rid of your thoughts,

00:57:03.800 --> 00:57:06.050
because if you
sit there and say,

00:57:06.050 --> 00:57:08.810
I'm going to try not to
think, you can't do that.

00:57:08.810 --> 00:57:10.610
Thoughts just jump around.

00:57:10.610 --> 00:57:12.650
And so till you get
rid of your thoughts,

00:57:12.650 --> 00:57:13.860
you go to this mantra.

00:57:13.860 --> 00:57:15.800
You repeat it over
and over again.

00:57:15.800 --> 00:57:18.840
And so when you pay
attention to that,

00:57:18.840 --> 00:57:20.750
you can't be thinking
about something.

00:57:20.750 --> 00:57:23.360
And then eventually
the mantra disappears,

00:57:23.360 --> 00:57:25.760
and you're in a
subconscious state.

00:57:25.760 --> 00:57:27.870
And when you're in that
subconscious state,

00:57:27.870 --> 00:57:30.590
you're neither conscious
or unconscious.

00:57:30.590 --> 00:57:33.830
You're in your
subconscious state.

00:57:33.830 --> 00:57:35.660
So it's relaxing,
and it's great,

00:57:35.660 --> 00:57:37.700
and it gives you
that equanimity.

00:57:37.700 --> 00:57:44.645
But it also is where creativity
comes from, because you

00:57:44.645 --> 00:57:45.860
don't muscle creativity.

00:57:45.860 --> 00:57:48.170
You don't say, I'm going
to work and get creative.

00:57:48.170 --> 00:57:49.610
It's more like relaxation.

00:57:49.610 --> 00:57:52.880
You take a hot shower, and
this great idea comes to you.

00:57:52.880 --> 00:57:55.250
So it bubbles up from
your subconscious.

00:57:55.250 --> 00:57:58.730
And so it enhances creativity.

00:57:58.730 --> 00:58:01.880
And also, I would say, one of
