01:07:05.230 --> 01:07:07.560
And some times I say
to myself, if you

01:07:07.560 --> 01:07:10.950
wrestle about which way to do it
so much and you struggle at it,

01:07:10.950 --> 01:07:12.480
you probably could
just flip a coin

01:07:12.480 --> 01:07:15.330
