not to do that is I

01:07:28.290 --> 01:07:33.450
instead make very clear
metrics and compensation levels

01:07:33.450 --> 01:07:38.220
by groups of people rather than
putting the particular names

01:07:38.220 --> 01:07:40.560
to that so that
everybody knows if you're

01:07:40.560 --> 01:07:42.840
doing this well with
that generalization,

01:07:42.840 --> 01:07:45.270
you know where the comp
levels are for others.

01:07:45.270 --> 01:07:48.420
And the reason I did that is
because when I found myself

01:07:48.420 --> 01:07:51.840
in discussions with,
is an evaluation

01:07:51.840 --> 01:07:56.140
of how that guy is
doing with other people.

01:07:56.140 --> 01:07:57.310
And that wasn't good.

01:07:57.310 --> 01:08:00.930
In other words, if all
of a sudden you say,

01:08:00.930 --> 01:08:03.840
Harry's earning this amount.

01:08:03.840 --> 01:08:07.147
And now I have to describe
my relationship and how

01:08:07.147 --> 01:08:08.730
