01:08:31.290 --> 01:08:33.430
exactly how radically
transparent,

01:08:33.430 --> 01:08:35.430
because I don't really
care too much about that.

01:08:35.430 --> 01:08:37.229
Do it either way is OK, fine.

01:08:37.229 --> 01:08:39.870
