OK, what about the taping?

01:08:42.960 --> 01:08:47.051
What about the those kinds of
idea meritocratic, those bigger

01:08:47.051 --> 01:08:47.550
issues?

01:08:47.550 --> 01:08:49.680
Because just like the
question before, OK,

01:08:49.680 --> 01:08:51.930
how do we do it,
OK, the big things

01:08:51.930 --> 01:08:53.760
you can we can
wrestle around here

01:08:53.760 --> 01:08:55.490
and how you choose
that individual thing.

01:08:55.490 --> 01:08:57.319
I'm just describing
