01:24:57.360 --> 01:25:00.630
and agree on together what
the best algorithms are

01:25:00.630 --> 01:25:02.490
so we can make that evolution.

01:25:02.490 --> 01:25:04.530
And, as I say, that probably--

01:25:04.530 --> 01:25:07.500
I don't know how many months--
